              <p class="text-muted">Environment Enthusiast</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Testimonial 2 -->
        <div class="col-md-4">
          <div class="card shadow-sm border-0">
            <div class="card-body text-center">
              <img
                src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/17302716/pexels-photo-17302716/free-photo-of-silhouette-of-a-man-standing-on-a-hill-at-sunset-with-his-arms-raised.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=600"
                class="rounded-circle mb-3" alt="User 2" style="width: 100px; height: 100px; object-fit: cover;">
              <p class="card-text">"The user-friendly interface and valuable resources make ecoBuddy my go-to platform
                for green living."</p>
              <h6 class="fw-bold mt-3">Ankit Verma</h6>
              <p class="text-muted">Eco Blogger</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Testimonial 3 -->
        <div class="col-md-4">
          <div class="card shadow-sm border-0">
            <div class="card-body text-center">
              <img
                src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/10678795/pexels-photo-10678795.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=600"
                class="rounded-circle mb-3" alt="User 3" style="width: 100px; height: 100px; object-fit: cover;">
              <p class="card-text">"Joining ecoBuddy connected me with a community of like-minded people. Highly
                recommended!"</p>
              <h6 class="fw-bold mt-3">Simran Kaur</h6>
              <p class="text-muted">Sustainability Advocate</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>